{"type": "article", "id": 26763, "title": "灵活组装的钥匙扣", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-13T06:34:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 83, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132457ypTJRSwNziXBjvkM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">钥匙的收纳有时也是件挺让人头疼的事：如果把钥匙都挂在同一个普通的钥匙扣上，在使用时不仅会制造出噪音，看上去也显得有些累赘。KEYDISK MINI 是一个可以容纳八把钥匙的钥匙扣，外观小巧别致，无论是组装还是拆卸起来都很方便。这款产品目前在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2129772055/keydisk-mini-a-smaller-more-minimal-solution\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，早鸟价为 12 美元。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132453cJrnASdU5ECIKRf0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132454wBfYugbdIzoTX6i0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132455eC0D9pTVivEGoP6L.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132455r40u1snveELdHZWf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}